+{"type":"message","id":"0c68bcda","parentId":"fd2b29e0","timestamp":"2026-03-26T05:42:46.985Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Plan overview:\n{\n  \"goal\": \"Build a RAG-powered AI insight agent for the Weekly Commit application. This includes Pinecone vector DB integration, OpenRouter embedding service, semantic search/query pipeline, proactive insight generation, event-driven indexing hooks, three new API endpoints, and frontend components (InsightPanel, SemanticSearchInput, QueryAnswerCard) wired into MyWeek and TeamWeek routes.\",\n  \"totalSteps\": 13,\n  \"stepTitles\": [\n    \"1. Add @EnableAsync and pinecone config to application.yml + test application.yml\",\n    \"2. Create EmbeddingService.java + EmbeddingServiceTest.java\",\n    \"3. Create PineconeClient.java + PineconeClientTest.java\",\n    \"4. Create ChunkBuilder.java + ChunkBuilderTest.java\",\n    \"5. Create SemanticIndexService.java + event-driven indexing hooks\",\n    \"6. Create SemanticQueryService.java + SemanticQueryServiceTest.java\",\n    \"7. Create InsightGenerationService.java + InsightGenerationServiceTest.java\",\n    \"8. Add RAG DTOs and new AiController endpoints\",\n    \"9. Create frontend API client and hooks for RAG endpoints\",\n    \"10. Create QueryAnswerCard.tsx + QueryAnswerCard.test.tsx\",\n    \"11. Create SemanticSearchInput.tsx + SemanticSearchInput.test.tsx\",\n    \"12. Create InsightPanel.tsx + InsightPanel.test.tsx\",\n    \"13. Wire InsightPanel and SemanticSearchInput into MyWeek.tsx and TeamWeek.tsx\"\n  ]\n}\n\nStep 8: Add RAG DTOs and new AiController endpoints\n{\n  \"id\": \"step-8\",\n  \"title\": \"Add RAG DTOs and new AiController endpoints\",\n  \"description\": \"Create DTOs in `backend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/dto/`:\\n- `RagQueryRequest.java` — record with `String question`, `UUID teamId` (optional), `UUID userId` (optional). Add `@NotBlank` on question.\\n- `RagQueryResponse.java` — record with `boolean aiAvailable`, `String answer`, `List<RagSourceDto> sources`, `double confidence`, `UUID suggestionId`.\\n- `RagSourceDto.java` — record with `String entityType`, `String entityId`, `String weekStartDate`, `String snippet`.\\n- `InsightCardDto.java` — record with `UUID suggestionId`, `String insightText`, `String severity`, `List<String> sourceEntityIds`, `String actionSuggestion`, `String createdAt`.\\n- `InsightListResponse.java` — record with `boolean aiAvailable`, `List<InsightCardDto> insights`.\\n\\nThe repository query methods added in step-1 (`findByTeamIdAndWeekStartDateAndSuggestionType` and the existing `findByPlanIdAndSuggestionType`) provide the data layer for these endpoints.\\n\\nAdd to `AiController.java`:\\n- `@PostMapping(\\\"/api/ai/query\\\")` — Validates request, calls `SemanticQueryService.query()`, maps to `RagQueryResponse`. Graceful degradation: if service returns unavailable, return `{aiAvailable: false}`.\\n- `@GetMapping(\\\"/api/teams/{id}/week/{weekStart}/ai-insights\\\")` — Calls `AiSuggestionRepository.findByTeamIdAndWeekStartDateAndSuggestionType(teamId, weekStart, \\\"TEAM_INSIGHT\\\")`. Parses each suggestion's `suggestionPayload` JSON into `InsightCardDto`. Returns `InsightListResponse`. Because step-1 added `team_id` and `week_start_date` columns and step-7 stores them on every TEAM_INSIGHT row, this query reliably returns the correct records.\\n- `@GetMapping(\\\"/api/plans/{id}/ai-insights\\\")` — Calls `AiSuggestionRepository.findByPlanIdAndSuggestionType(planId, \\\"PERSONAL_INSIGHT\\\")`. Parses payload into `InsightCardDto`. Returns `InsightListResponse`.\\n\\nImport and inject `SemanticQueryService` and `AiSuggestionRepository` into AiController constructor.\\n\\nEnsure all endpoints follow the existing graceful degradation pattern (try/catch wrapping, returning aiAvailable: false on any exception).\",\n  \"requiredChecks\": [\n    \"build\",\n    \"unit\"\n  ]\n}\n\nThis is relay round 2. Another agent has already worked on this step.\n\nYou are in VERIFICATION MODE. Your default action is to APPROVE.\nFocus your review on the DIFF — the changes made in the previous round.\nOnly make changes if there is a MATERIAL defect: failing check, missing step requirement, logic bug, or security issue.\nStyle preferences, alternative approaches, comment wording, and optional polish are NOT grounds for changes.\n\nIf all checks pass and the step requirements are met, approve immediately.\nLog anything else you notice as observations — do not act on them.\n\nPrevious agent's notes:\nFull build passes. Here's a summary of everything done:\n\n## Summary\n\n### DTOs created (`backend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/dto/`)\n\n- **`RagQueryRequest.java`** — Record with `@NotBlank String question`, optional `UUID teamId`, optional `UUID userId`\n- **`RagSourceDto.java`** — Record with `String entityType`, `entityId`, `weekStartDate`, `snippet`\n- **`RagQueryResponse.java`** — Record with `boolean aiAvailable`, `String answer`, `List<RagSourceDto> sources`, `double confidence`, `UUID suggestionId`; includes `unavailable()` factory\n- **`InsightCardDto.java`** — Record with `UUID suggestionId`, `String insightText`, `severity`, `List<String> sourceEntityIds`, `actionSuggestion`, `createdAt`\n- **`InsightListResponse.java`** — Record with `boolean aiAvailable`, `List<InsightCardDto> insights`; includes `unavailable()` factory\n\n### `AiController.java` updated\n\nNew injected dependencies: `SemanticQueryService`, `AiSuggestionRepository`, `ObjectMapper`\n\nThree new endpoints:\n1. **`POST /api/ai/query`** — Calls `SemanticQueryService.query()`, maps `RagQueryResult` → `RagQueryResponse`; returns `aiAvailable: false` on any exception\n2. **`GET /api/teams/{id}/week/{weekStart}/ai-insights`** — Queries `findByTeamIdAndWeekStartDateAndSuggestionType(..., \"TEAM_INSIGHT\")`, parses each `suggestionPayload` JSON into `InsightCardDto`\n3. **`GET /api/plans/{id}/ai-insights`** — Queries `findByPlanIdAndSuggestionType(..., \"PERSONAL_INSIGHT\")`, same parsing\n\nPrivate `parseInsightCards()` helper extracts `insightText`, `severity`, `actionSuggestion`, `sourceEntityIds` from the JSON payload and `createdAt` from the entity timestamp; unparseable rows are silently skipped.\n\n### `AiControllerTest.java` updated\n\nAdded `@MockBean SemanticQueryService` and `@MockBean AiSuggestionRepository` so the `@WebMvcTest` context can build the updated `AiController`.\n\nVerdict: changes_made\n\nFiles changed so far:\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/cost.json\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/sessions/continuous/relay-a/2026-03-26T04-47-46-137Z_72092699-d416-4051-8917-7a32e149dfa5.jsonl\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/state.json\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/controller/AiController.java\nbackend/src/test/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/controller/AiControllerTest.java\n.pi/duet/runs/2026-03-26T04-36-08-591Z-21100373/steps/8\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/dto/InsightCardDto.java\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/dto/InsightListResponse.java\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/dto/RagQueryRequest.java\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/dto/RagQueryResponse.java\nbackend/src/main/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/dto/RagSourceDto.java\n\nWhen done, explain what you reviewed, what you changed (if anything), and your assessment.\n\nEnd with:\nVerdict: approve  — if the step is complete and correct, no more changes needed\nVerdict: changes_made  — if you made fixes or improvements\nVerdict: replan_needed  — if the step is structurally impossible to complete as planned and needs controller-managed replanning"}],"timestamp":1774503766984}}
